{"tid":713711,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"搭個𨋢都咁辛苦","createTime":"2018-06-23T05:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T05:25:23.000Z","uid":94055,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c0b7f16b6d0a4d49aebeb229fecf3bde78d3029e","tid":713711,"uid":94055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T05:14:19.000Z","msg":"琴日出咗陣街 回程就地鐵翻歸啦<br />\n何文田地鐵站十幾廿層<br />\n懶得行嘅我就搭𨋢上大堂<br />\n只要你去開何文田站 就知一定行上一層換𨋢搭最方便<br />\n<br />\n咁我就去等𨋢啦 隔咗陣有個女仔又過黎等<br />\n示意圖(大概係咁嘅髮型 唔太記得)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/131340_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F131340_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b65c325b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本身部𨋢裡面都冇乜人 得一對夫婦 大概三十零歲<br />\n臨柵門嗰時突然有班外籍阿姐衝入黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 心諗部𨋢咁細 點再放你哋七八個人呀 等下架啦唔該<br />\n點知佢哋死逼爛逼 夾硬黎 又俾佢哋入曬<br />\n搞到成部𨋢啲人逼到實先上去<br />\n<br />\n個女仔本身企我前面<br />\n結果逼到我條J貼住佢個籮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁大個仔都未試過同人咁近距離接觸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我梗係即刻咬牙 忍住啲慾念<br />\n如果唔小心chok一chok起反應咁就仆街了<br />\n<br />\n捱過幾層嘅尷尬之後終於上大堂<br />\n仆你個街 班阿姐仲企係度傾計 驚出錯𨋢<br />\n對夫婦都忍唔住叫佢哋借開出𨋢<br />\n我跟手快快腳走咗 唔敢回頭望個女仔即刻閃人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/130301_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F130301_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=9e8dda7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/130308_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F130308_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=5be2d6d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4286b9c45920aa45b99bcd950119754218e3cc28","tid":713711,"uid":94055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T05:21:27.000Z","msg":"勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1fa5763660fd6c46baccd6fe899c415ad2668ee","tid":713711,"uid":136699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T05:23:41.000Z","msg":"大大聲屌9啲啊婆咪得囉<br />\n死咸濕仔係咪想非禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd1d7ff36ce148c3fb95b78c405365a4ce3e4358","tid":713711,"uid":147789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T05:25:23.000Z","msg":"最近留長咗頭髮<br />\n唔知係咪個背影太似女仔<br />\n成日都feel到有牙籤仔拮我屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身諗住話比佢知我係個boy <br />\n點知佢就急急腳咁走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}